gottengeography (1.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Robert Bruce Park ]
  * Remember map sources in gconf. Closes #52
  * Use GtkRadioMenuItems for the map source menu.
  * String cleanup.
  * Version 1.2.1!
  * Move map source logic into PreferencesController.

  [ Marc Ordinas i Llopis ]
  * Use python-distutils-extra to manage i18n.

  [ Robert Bruce Park ]
  * Fix bug where lookup_geoname() sometimes fails.
  * Allow provincestate to be None in pretty_geoname()
  * Add geolocation to window titlebar. Closes #44.
  * Drop bdist_rpm.
  * Expand test suite to test the new window title feature.
  * Add new test to cover the recent bugfix in lookup_geoname().
  * Reduce redundancy in pretty_geoname() and test it better.
  * Test for ability to change map sources.

  [ Marc Ordinas i Llopis ]
  * Imported Upstream version 1.2.1
  * Added python-distutils-extra to Build-Depends.

